  "text": "Monsoon Fury: Home Ministry releases Rs 1,066 crore for six flood-hit states\nIn a message on X, Union Home Minister Amit Shah said, \"More than Rs 8,000 crore from SDRF/NDRF funds has been provided to 19 states this year. Apart from financial aid, providing all logistic assistance, including deployment of requisite NDRF, Army, and Air Force, has been our priority.\"\nThis year, the Centre has already released Rs 6,166.00 crore from SDRF to 14 states and Rs 1,988.91 crore from National Disaster Response Fund (NDRF) to 12 states. Image: Pexels",
